{"title":"嘱路边小树","authors":["鲁琪"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":1,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘱路边小树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲁琪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫长的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥远的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在太累了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就让我睡在这里吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍着这棵路边的小树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（可不能睡在路当中呵这会有碍别人的脚步）。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睡下了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不听风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不望月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你嫩绿的枝丫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我搭座小屋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噢，不是小屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是座绿色的坟墓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（可不要招来小鸟为我啼哭！）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，小树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你记住！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你长成了参天大树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是我的肢体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已深深钻入泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个细胞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都把你的根须紧紧攥住。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}